<title>USA: CCB completes Salem merger.</title>
<headline>CCB completes Salem merger.</headline>
<dateline>DURHAM, N.C. 1997-02-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>CCB Financial Corp said Monday it has completed the acquisition of Salem Trust Bank of Winston-Salem, N.C.</p>
<p>The final exchange ratio is 0.36 share of CCB Financial common stock for each share of Salem Trust Bank common stock, CCB said.  ((-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610.))</p>
